Package org.goplanit.utils.graph

Interface Edge

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Comparable<IdAble>, ExternalIdAble, GraphEntity, IdAble, ManagedId, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ConnectoidEdge, DirectedEdge, Link, ServiceLeg
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConnectoidEdgeImpl, DirectedEdgeImpl, EdgeImpl, LinkImpl, ServiceLegImpl
    public interface Edge
extends Serializable, GraphEntity
    Edge interface connecting two vertices in a non-directional fashion.
